Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種…應該叫做『Koper轉』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Kopernikanische回轉』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}（德）Kopernikanische回轉：與歷來哲學相反 客觀從屬主觀的觀點回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\1cH000000\fad(100,500)}美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚？神樂坂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對方好像是營銷部的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前碰到她時  還說沒有正在交往的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真信了她的話啊  春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是故意不讓人知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  被騙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下可不是笑的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我就不可能隱瞞起來麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.81,0:02:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳又不會撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿  暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不渴望結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相親之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為嘛…現在還是看小說比較有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說工作是編輯  結果還不是只被差使複印東西啦倒茶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和OL沒什麼區別啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  這才是我工作的第三年嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西  這個每張複印十份  麻煩妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是第三年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西妳很喜歡美川煌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是他的大FAN
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中時還給他寫了慕名信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的擔當(編輯)  從今天起由妳來做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法了 上吧 弥次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 喜多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你們所願 抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}小心點  我現在很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『弥次喜多』麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這部電影裡那個時代男人間肝膽相照的友情  真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有做作的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  姊姊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹  妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  其實有本想借的書(惡搞自謙語)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有了喜歡的男生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼類型的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小夏想看書的時候就是有了喜歡的人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.11,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看同一本書對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏總是喜歡上很聰明的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反正就是喜歡和自己個性相反的類型啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  是什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人雖然跟我是同班同學  已經是4年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  成為美川煌老師的擔當了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  第一次當作家的擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  本來就是他的FAN  緊張死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野島  要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話跟我說？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  一副幸福得要死的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是有不幸的存在  幸福才格外顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為不幸的根源還有資格問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊  我還不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  居然無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是這次的收信人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰啊  難得看到文伽有那種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著時和他有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著時  我對他開了槍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲料沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶點沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和姊姊上班
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是關於文歌的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為這事  他怎麼會找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊  妳不是去上班了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是鬧鐘停了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳把鬧鐘按了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  直接去美川煌老師那裡  還趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…提早了一點來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好一個知書達禮的文科少年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的夏香就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢惹哭她  我會好好教訓你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走咯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在住院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  他在家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是繞段路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…很重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事想拜託妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於美川的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是  我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說被文歌拒絕過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是打算再次告白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到美川了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不應該見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為美川她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在沉睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前開始就一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是見到了  或許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然相似的別的什麼人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼跟文伽長得一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  我的另一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「另一部分」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,槍擊父親和這件事難道有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼美川會對自己的父親開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有甦醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是正在KISS什麼的  真的抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記去煌老師家的地圖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能用手機發過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我房間裡有掃瞄儀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會用什麼掃瞄儀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夏  謝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳姊姊是美川煌的擔當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近剛成為的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才發去的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去見美川煌親自確認美川的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然美川無法甦醒  知道真相的就只有美川煌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(284,80)}美川煌老師家的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(284,147)}無邊無際的銀色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(594,80)}在森林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(554,173)}石橋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(554,240)}街道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(338,213)}地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(338,280)}汽車站
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\bord0\shad0\1cH000000}{\pos(513,413)}海鷗市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無邊無際的…銀色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 千惠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都四年沒出了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說得事不關己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出了  肯定可以賣80萬冊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔當交給年輕的社員了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個據說很沒用的…沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「誰知道啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正她本來就很沒用  用壞了也不可惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個  初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯田橋出版第一編輯部的葛西春乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了  新的擔當  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美川煌  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我要去見美川煌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我想見妳一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮  都是玻璃筆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起金屬製的筆  用這些我能寫得更美些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到亮處去聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著的時間的連續
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸其中  才是無上的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃的…閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭文字處理機啊圓珠筆啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它們不美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我把原稿拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天在展示會上展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  還沒倒茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有上好的香草茶  稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}光明中的閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽說作家中有很多怪人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是因為我是從來不讀書的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  文歌對於自己一直被看作美川煌的女兒感到厭倦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川煌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我對演歌沒什麼興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說錯了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  開始經常和文歌說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌是個少言寡語的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天都待在學校的保健室裡  她的事具體我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只是」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只問過我一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我「夏香的父親是什麼樣的人？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  原來那麼大受好評嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人吃驚  一處重寫的地方都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些連草稿都沒打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然老師很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為構思階段花了大量的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能否讓我參觀下您的工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作室？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼美麗的原稿  是在哪寫成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作室很髒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思見人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明預報是10%的可能性的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是太陽雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明出太陽了  還下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽雨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨  閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明出太陽了  明明出太陽了  明明出太陽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  小心感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  妳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽雨  太陽雨喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過的呢  這種電影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  起舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  停了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好一場阻礙前進的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼抽象模糊的目的地  叫我到哪找美川煌的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}無邊無際的銀色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就不渴望結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀色之路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來尺寸很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這是誰的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來猜猜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵遞員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收下了  我收下了  我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慕名信嗎  真懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也跟老師您寫過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到了回信  感激不已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是進了公司才知道  那是編輯回的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  信能讓我看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種字  是中學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  煌老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫銀色的Njord
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs21}Njord：出自北歐神話 神分為兩個部族 以主神奧丁(Odin)為首領的阿薩神族(Aesir)\N以及以大海之神尼約德(Njord)為首領的華納神族(Vanir)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讀了老師所有的書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數次地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗而殘酷  最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後的世界如同冰雪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生命  沒有色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲  細菌  沒有任何污垢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終極潔淨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死  並不悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清靜  美麗的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.39,0:19:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直認為只有黑暗和恐懼的死後的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種…應該叫做『Koper轉』吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Kopernikanische回轉』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從死後的世界寄來的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以稱為死後文
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖的火焰
